{"id":147326,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/也门反政府人士要求总统立即下台/","date":"2011-04-24T23:30:32Z","modified":"2011-04-24T23:30:32Z","title":"也门反政府人士要求总统立即下台","content":"<div>\n<p>萨那</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>也门总统萨利赫虽然原则上同意下台，但是该国首都的抗议活动仍在持续。数千名反政府人士仍旧坚守在首都萨那的一个中心广场上。他们说，他们要求萨利赫立即下台的要求并没有得到满足。萨利赫周六表示,同意海湾合作委员会提出的建议，30天内将国家权力移交给副总统。但他的条件是，下台后不会受到任何刑事处罚。据政府批评人士说，在东南部的贝达省(Al –Beidha)，萨利赫的共和国卫队同当地武装居民发生枪战。6名卫队士兵以及3名平民丧生。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C6511861%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%B9%9F%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}